introduction.en-US: Vỹ Pekkala is an EREPS-certified Personal Trainer EQF level 4 based in Helsinki Finland with 2 years of coaching experience.

body.en-US:
You’re not here for a basic workout.
You’re here for something deeper.
You want to feel strong—not just in your body, but in your mind.
You want to move with intention, live with confidence, and fully show up as the most powerful version of you.
At SlayFit Vili, we mix movement, mindset, and a whole lot of magic.
This isn’t about punishing your body—it’s about honoring it.
Building strength from the inside out. Creating space for growth, clarity, and real transformation.
 ✨ This is personal training, but elevated.
 ✨ It’s fierce, fabulous, and grounded in self-awareness.
 ✨ It’s fitness that feels good in your soul.
We’ll work hard, yes—but we’ll also laugh, vibe, reflect, and celebrate the hell out of your progress.
No pressure to be perfect. No toxic hustle. Just you, showing up for yourself in the most powerful way.
Because when your mindset shifts, your whole life starts to shift with it.
You ready to step into your power? Let’s slay.
